        {
            "id": 6289213,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 大眾控(3701)大漲8.01%，報52.6元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大眾控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3701:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3701\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3701-TW</a>)26日12:54股價上漲3.9元，報52.6元，漲幅8.01%，成交28,180張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大眾控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3701:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3701\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3701-TW</a>)所屬產業為電腦及週邊設備業，主要業務為H201010一般投資業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲35.65%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.29%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,723 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,683 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+40 張</li> <li>融資增減：+2,959 張</li> <li>融券增減：+638 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
